sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Look Graph Webview
participant Router as GraphMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as GetGraphDataUseCase
participant Repo as GitRepository implements RepositoryOperationCapabilities
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

User->>App: Open Look Graph
App->>Router: graph/dataRequest(repositoryLocator, PageRequest, filters, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Repo
Router->>UseCase: execute(Repo, filters, PageRequest, signal)
par Commit graph
  UseCase->>Repo: getCommitGraph(filters, PageRequest, signal)
and Branches and tags
  UseCase->>Repo: listBranches(signal)
  UseCase->>Repo: listTags(signal)
and Worktrees and submodules
  UseCase->>Repo: listWorktrees(signal)
  UseCase->>Repo: listSubmodules(signal)
end
Repo->>Runtime: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, PageRequest, signal)
Repo->>Runtime: listBranches(executionContext, signal)
Repo->>Runtime: listTags(executionContext, signal)
Repo->>Runtime: listWorktrees(executionContext, signal)
Repo->>Runtime: listSubmodules(executionContext, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, PageRequest, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: listBranches(executionContext, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: listTags(executionContext, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: listWorktrees(executionContext, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: listSubmodules(executionContext, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: graph domain values
Runtime-->>Repo: graph domain values
Repo-->>UseCase: graph domain values
UseCase-->>Router: GraphData
Router-->>App: graph/dataResponse(requestId, GraphData)
App-->>User: Render graph
